                                                                <customfield id="customfield_12310192" key="com.atlassian.jira.plugin.system.customfieldtypes:textarea">
                        <customfieldname>Release Note</customfieldname>
                        <customfieldvalues>
                            <customfieldvalue>This patch introduced a new configuration &amp;quot;hbase.balancer.tablesOnMaster&amp;quot; to control what tables&amp;#39; regions should be put on the master by a load balancer. By default, we will put regions of table acl, namespace, and meta on master, i.e. the default configuration is the same as &amp;quot;hbase:acl,hbase:namespace,hbase:meta&amp;quot;. To put no region on the master, you need to set &amp;quot;hbase.balancer.tablesOnMaster&amp;quot; to &amp;quot;none&amp;quot; instead of an empty string(the default will be used if it is empty).</customfieldvalue>

                        </customfieldvalues>
